---- ALGORITHMS ----
>> C2: Explain how you read and write to the console for the kernel monitor.

Used the standard `printf` to write back to the console and used the `input_getc` function to retrieve the next character for every key press (upto 80 chars).

>> C3: Any additional enhancement you implement?

Support for backspaces in case user mistypes an input.